LAGOS – Fast-rising singer, Fope Okuyiga who has always serenaded his fans with great tunes by proving his worth has finally released his first body of work. According to him, the body of work will further confirm that he is not in the game for jokes, as he has confirmed that he is currently working on more songs. “The first body of work has been released and I am not relenting, I am working on more songs because it’s not a joke anymore. I’m here to make a statement. Titled ‘Greatness’, the body of work has four tracks and expresses the lifestyle, experiences and pursuits of the budding singer. His words: “I am happy that the body of work has hit the internet and I feel great just like the title of the EP, Greatness. I was able to express my thoughts inspired by different happenings, experiences and pursuits which I’m confident that people will love.” However, since the release of the EP, Okuyiga, has been receiving applauds from fans for a job well done, given his ability to come up with such a wonderful collection of songs.